        A full constructor for the crime object
        Parameters:
        category - the category of the crime in url slug form
        persistent_id - the UUID for the crime which can be used for tracking
        location_type - the type of the location attached to the crime
        location_subtype - the subtype of the location attached to the crime
        id - an internal ID (PK?) of the crime, use persistent_id for tracking
        location - location attached to the crime
        context - extra information about the crime
        outcome_status - outcome status
